node.text: Quinn Ewers, the top-rated quarterback in the 2022 Class, who arrived on campus Saturday and will begin practicing for Ohio State today, has signed with agencies Sportstars Inc. (@sportstarsnyc ) and Rubicon Talent (@rubicontalent ) for NIL representation. Agents Ron Slavin, Emil Boccio (Sportstars) and Dave Maryles (Rubicon Talent) will lead the efforts for Ewers as he embarks on his intercollegiate football career at Ohio State.
